{"tid":2414045,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"WhatsApp 私隱條款再更新　不會與FB分享聯絡人 + 私人訊息","createTime":"2021-02-19T06:32:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-19T08:11:18.000Z","uid":28114,"like":1,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"e5d93b7b2d50bc1fad0e7a95894692f67556ddc9","tid":2414045,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T06:32:47.000Z","msg":"WhatsApp 在今年年初更新私隱條款，導致不少用家擔心其數據會被分享至 Facebook 用作置入廣告，更有不少人「跳槽」至其他服務。WhatsApp 後來延長期限後，最近再推出新的條款通知，希望用更詳盡的方式解釋新條款。<br />\n<br />\nWhatsApp 表示，過去數星期一直了解用戶對於新條款的意見，知道用戶希望了解在新條款底下數據會否仍然首端對端加密保護，其對話又會否被第三方存取，平台會否保留訊息記錄和聯絡人名單等。而 WhatsApp 決定提供新的通知，利用由淺入深的方式詳細解釋新的服務條款和私隱政策。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/WhatsApp_Screens.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2FWhatsApp_Screens.jpg&h=ad53f173&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nWhatsApp 強調，新服務條款和私隱政策不會更改個人對話的私隱，而且只與商業業務功能有關，在新條款下用戶可以自行決定是否與商戶聯絡，選擇向商戶提供的內容。新的通知將會在幾個星期後開始向用戶推送，屆時 App 上將會出現一個小橫額，按下連結可以看到政策內容。目前 WhatsApp 將接受更新條款的期限延長至 5 月 15 日，讓用戶有更充足的時間去閱讀和理解條款。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2021/02/19/whatsapp-new-policy-notification/fun-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2021%2F02%2F19%2Fwhatsapp-new-policy-notification%2Ffun-tech%2F&d=VW1JDW%2BJF%2FyRlCRofLrhGvolgVFqTZkzW3om5iGclzM%3D&h=df79fa01\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2021/02/19/whatsapp-new-policy-notification/fun-tech/</a>"},{"pid":"616c032cd4ce0c92822b5a6c78dac0b6c2a06ce2","tid":2414045,"uid":292700,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T06:33:59.000Z","msg":"收皮啦 已轉晒用signal<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3524521a70ac1c1f80389b38a0d93d9abae04a71","tid":2414045,"uid":76609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T06:34:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fa